ABW (Automatically Birthday Wishing ) will help us to automate the process of liking and commenting on each birthday post without toiling away on facebook of hour.
like let'us say it's your birthday .You are super excited and spend the day having your party.The next morning you log on to the facebook and find that your timeline completely
flooded with birthday post from all your well-wishers.You want to reply to all of them,but it would take you all day,but this can easily done by the ABW.



